<package name="lsiommu" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>List IOMMU groups and their devices</title>
  <description>A hardware inspection utility that shows the relationships between IOMMU groups, physical PCIe hardware, and nested USB buses.

It is commonly used when setting up Kernel-based Virtual Machines (KVM) with VFIO hardware passthrough (i.e., PCIe passthrough of a host device, such as a graphics card or a network interface) to a guest VM.
</description>
</package>
